Job brief
We are looking for a qualified Sales Administrator to join our team. You will serve as a point of contact for customers with queries about products, orders and deliveries and provide support for and report to the sales director.
Our ideal candidate is goal-oriented and has a deep knowledge of customer service best practices. If you have exceptional organizational skills and draw energy from being part of a team, we would like to meet you.
Ultimately, you should be able to contribute to high quality customer service

Responsibilities
 Process customer orders via email or phone
 Handle &amp; Check data accuracy in orders and invoices
 Contact clients to obtain missing information or answer queries
 Coordinate with Production Department on the customer뭩 order
 Liaise with the Logistics department to ensure timely deliveries
 Maintain and update sales and customer records
 Develop monthly sales reports
 Communicate important feedback from customers internally
 Tally and monitor outstanding A/R with customers